---
title: Sicilian-Style Salmon & Herby Caper Sauce with Panzanella Salad & Roasted Potatoes
description: You're going to love this one – the aroma of the herby caper sauce against the succulent salmon is mind-blowingly good. With
roasted veggies, plus creamy goat cheese and crispy croutons in the Panzanella salad, we reckon it's destined for greatness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sicilian-style-salmon-herby-caper-sauce-9816ba7e.jpg
